{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add pulses (peas, chickpeas, lentils etc) to food label allergen requirements",
        "additional_details": "With pulses not being one of the 14 allergens, packaging DOES NOT highlight when pulses are an ingredient.\r\n \r\nThere are A LOT of people allergic to pulses and I would love to make a difference and see pulses added to the list of allergens that must be listed on food labels, to make it 15 allergens!",
        "background": "I have found that many shops, businesses, food facilities are now trying to make a lot of their foods gluten free, which is great for Celiacs but can be a massive problem for people who are allergic to pulses, which are often used as substitutes for wheat. PULSES NEED TO BE HIGHLIGHTED.",
